<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>droneOS</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">**droneOS**<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>proprietary,<sp/>ROS<sp/>2-based<sp/>modular<sp/>SDK<sp/>for<sp/>commanding<sp/>PX4-compatible<sp/>autonomous<sp/>drone<sp/>fleets.<sp/>It<sp/>provides<sp/>reusable<sp/>mission<sp/>logic,<sp/>low-level<sp/>PX4<sp/>communication,<sp/>and<sp/>real-time<sp/>control<sp/>infrastructure<sp/>for<sp/>scalable,<sp/>multi-agent<sp/>operations.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>‚úàÔ∏è<sp/>Features</highlight></codeline>
