<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>Fleet-level<sp/>drone<sp/>management<sp/>via<sp/>`DroneAgent`<sp/>and<sp/>`DroneManager`</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>YAML-driven<sp/>waypoint<sp/>missions<sp/>with<sp/>auto-progress<sp/>logic</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>Real-time<sp/>position<sp/>tracking<sp/>using<sp/>PX4<sp/>telemetry</highlight></codeline>
